152
00:09:30,913 --> 00:09:34,083
It sounds funny, but it's
really painful to debug later.

153
00:09:34,263 --> 00:09:40,933
Debugging becomes harder, and you do not
know on how it… You do not only need to

154
00:09:40,943 --> 00:09:46,073
