understand and fix the generated structure

155
00:09:46,163 --> 00:09:50,333
around it, and it take it can take one
day just to debug some simple stuff.

156
00:09:50,843 --> 00:09:52,163
So be very careful.

157
00:09:52,193 --> 00:09:56,043
AI can move fast, but without
architecture, it moves in every

158
00:09:56,043 --> 00:09:59,613
direction at once Another thing is UI.

159
00:10:00,213 --> 00:10:04,583
UI should be consistent before
you begin image implementation.

160
00:10:05,143 --> 00:10:11,533
Because one of the most visible problem
is AI-generated, in by AI-generated in

161
00:10:11,533 --> 00:10:13,793
the application is UI inconsistency.

162
00:10:13,793 --> 00:10:19,103
AI is very good at building a screen
from a screenshot or a description, but

163
00:10:19,103 --> 00:10:23,583
if every screen is treated as a separate
task, every screen may get its own

164
00:10:23,583 --> 00:10:26,733
style, and it happened with me a lot.

165
00:10:27,363 --> 00:10:31,453
I had different back buttons, different
navigation animations, different bottom

166
00:10:31,453 --> 00:10:34,193
