170
00:10:43,863 --> 00:10:45,923
This is where product vision matters.

171
00:10:45,963 --> 00:10:49,163
You need to know how your app should feel.

172
00:10:49,503 --> 00:10:52,843
Navigation, loading, error
handling, empty state, spacing,

173
00:10:52,873 --> 00:10:54,413
colors, typography, animation.

174
00:10:54,763 --> 00:10:59,433
AI can build UI components, but it
does not automatically understand

175
00:11:00,033 --> 00:11:01,893
the tactile feeling of your product.

176
00:11:02,293 --> 00:11:05,163
If you do not define the style,
the model will define it for you

177
00:11:05,323 --> 00:11:08,293
one screen at a time, and at the
end of the day, it will be a mess.

178
00:11:08,323 --> 00:11:12,823
And again, debugging sessions, finding
each components, it will take ton of

179
00:11:12,823 --> 00:11:18,313
time from you another huge problem,
but it's hidden, especially from the

180
00:11:18,313 --> 00:11:20,673
beginning, it's understanding of the code.

181
00:11:21,343 --> 00:11:25,043
It's the biggest f- problem
I found with the code because

182
00:11:25,063 --> 00:11:28,093
it wasn't the code quality, it
was understanding of this code.

183
00:11:28,683 --> 00:11:29,893
Sometimes the code works.

184
00:11:29,953 --> 00:11:35,153
Tests are green, the AI looks fine, but
you do not fully understand why it works.

185
00:11:35,403 --> 00:11:38,443
In enterprise, this reduces ownership.

186
00:11:38,883 --> 00:11:42,953
In the project, it creates painful
debugging session, and both of those are

187
00:11:43,483 --> 00:11:45,643
huge pain and very important to have.

188
00:11:46,163 --> 00:11:50,253
You may need to read thousand lines
of generated code to understand why

189
00:11:50,713 --> 00:11:55,803
